    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with its high-pressure VANOS system recently overhauled. This specimen retains its factory-correct subframe integrity and features a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission paired with a limited-slip variable M differential. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Meticulously maintained with a documented history of valve adjustments and fluid analysis, this vehicle delivers a visceral, high-revving linear power delivery and razor-sharp steering feedback. A pristine example for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical harmony.",
      "price": 48500.0,
